\newlabel{fig:operators_main}{{5}{15}{\textbf {Operator-level intuition for \swing {}.} The inflated fit operator \(\hat A_\tau \) says which directions the source data trusts after isotropic certification inflation. The fragility operator \(\hat B\) says which directions swing under source-support redistributions. Their generalized eigensystem defines the contraction geometry}{figure.caption.14}{}}
